Description: This dataset is composed of events and media descriptions associated with these events. It is obtained from three large public event directories (last.fm- eventful and upcoming) represented with the LODE ontology and from large media directories (flickr- youtube) represented with the W3C Media Ontology. It is interlinked with the larger Linked Open Data cloud and in particular with DBpedia- Freebase- Geonames. It also contains links to numerous related web pages- including MusicBrainz- Geonames- Last.fm- Eventful- Upcoming and Foursquare.
